    <h1>Conversation Intelligence</h1>
    <p class="description">AI-powered software that records, transcribes, and analyses every sales and customer conversation. Teams using it close deals <strong>15-25% more often</strong> than teams without.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
